examples: We finally traced him to an address in Chicago.
Finalmente lo rastreamos hasta una dirección en Chicago.
I have been unable to trace the letter you mentioned.
No he podido rastrear la carta que mencionaste.
She could trace her family tree back to the 16th century.
Podía rastrear su árbol genealógico hasta el siglo XVI.
The leak was eventually traced to a broken seal.
Finalmente, la fuga se atribuyó a un sello roto.
